Package: watchteleboy
Architecture: all
Depends: python3,
         python3-crontab,
         python3-requests,
         ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: mpv,
            ffmpeg
Suggests: tvbrowser
Description: Watch  and record TV streams from teleboy.ch
 Simple program to watch and record teleboy.ch IPTV streams:
  * No additional ads
  * No flash nor web browser required
  * allows streams to be recorded
  * supports live pause and seeking (e.g. for skipping commercials)
  * can watch or record shows up to three hours after air-time.
